data.description: This amazing 5 bedroom, 3 bath home located in Fox Ridge subdivision, in highly sought-after Coweta County is one you do not want to miss! This charming home offers plenty of space for entertaining, relaxing, and everything in between! Come check out the beautiful open kitchen, complete with granite countertops and hardwood floors throughout the downstairs. Wonderful flowing floor plan into the living and outdoor space; perfect for friends and family to enjoy together. The spacious master has a sitting area with a gas fireplace, a large walk-in closet, as well as a master bath with a double vanity and separate shower and tub. Rear patio that leads to a wonderful fenced, level backyard. Call The Charles Davis Team for more information before this one is gone!
